<p>
  Over the years I have worked across a wide range of creative and technical roles at Holosuite
  Media, including Executive Producer, host, audio engineer, editor, livestream operator,
  publisher, technical administrator, and automation/workflow support.
</p>
<p>
  The project combines many of my interests in technology, creativity, storytelling,
  automation, and online communities.
</p>

<h2>
  <i class="fa-solid fa-gears" aria-hidden="true"></i>
  <span>Technical work</span></h2>
<p>
  On the technical side, I have worked on livestream infrastructure, publishing workflows,
  automation systems, website management, media encoding, social distribution, hosting,
  infrastructure, and workflow optimisation.
</p>
<p>
  A large amount of this work has been about making media production more reliable and
  sustainable, especially when working with volunteers, remote hosts, different tools, and
  community-driven schedules.
</p>

<h2>
  <i class="fa-solid fa-paintbrush" aria-hidden="true"></i>
  <span>Creative work</span></h2>
<p>
  On the creative side, I have worked on podcast production, audio editing, livestream
  overlays, branding, video editing, creator support, and community management. Holosuite
  Media has also provided opportunities to support and collaborate with creators,
  communities, and fandoms across science fiction, fantasy, gaming, and online media spaces.
</p>

